column1: OMAP-20: Organ Mapping Antibody Panel (OMAP) for Multiplexed Antibody-Based Imaging of kidney with cyclic multiplexed immunofluorescence

column2: Andrea J. Radtke; Diane C. Saunders; Ellen M. Quardokus

column24: This marker defines the tubular basement membrane, mesangial matrix, and glomerular capsule.
This marker defines the glomerular basement membrane, glomerular capsule, and collecting duct and distal convoluted tubule basement membrane.
This marker defines mesangial and vascular smooth muscle cells.
This marker defines podocytes, specifically marking the cytoplasm and plasma membrane.
